		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<P>I've been called for jury duty twice so far and haven't gotten to hear a case yet.</P>
<P>The first time I was a fresh faced 18 year old.&nbsp; As most lawyers will tell you, kids just out of high school are usually not high on their list of who they want on their juries.&nbsp; It's just a matter of the lack of life experience.</P>
<P>The second time, the case got settled before the selection process even began.&nbsp; A group had been called in and filled out questionnaires, but that was it.</P>
<DIV></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							Yanari, Witch of Felwithe
							</div>
								
